<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>Affidavit of Truth — {{client.fullName}} — {{bureau.displayName}}</title>
<style>
  @page { size: Letter; margin: 0.85in 1in; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
    color: #000;
    font-size: 11.5pt;
    line-height: 1.45;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .from, .meta, .to {
    margin-bottom: 14pt;
  }
  .from div, .to div { line-height: 1.3; }
  .date { margin: 14pt 0; }
  .titles {
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 18pt 0 14pt 0;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .titles div { margin-bottom: 2pt; }
  .opening { margin-bottom: 12pt; text-align: justify; }
  .items {
    margin: 0 0 14pt 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .item {
    margin: 0 0 10pt 0;
    padding-left: 0;
  }
  .item-creditor {
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .item-detail {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #222;
  }
  .shared-reason {
    margin: 10pt 0 14pt 0;
    text-align: justify;
  }
  .pi-section { margin-top: 12pt; }
  .pi-list { padding-left: 18pt; margin: 6pt 0 14pt 0; }
  .pi-list li { margin-bottom: 6pt; }
  .demand {
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 14pt 0;
    text-align: justify;
  }
  .enclosed {
    margin: 12pt 0;
  }
  .enclosed ul {
    padding-left: 18pt;
    margin: 6pt 0;
  }
  .enclosed li { margin-bottom: 4pt; }
  .closing { margin: 12pt 0; text-align: justify; }
  .longform { margin: 12pt 0; text-align: justify; }
  .sign-off { margin-top: 28pt; }
  .signature-line {
    margin-top: 36pt;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    width: 320pt;
  }
  .signature-name {
    margin-top: 4pt;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="from">
  <div>{{client.fullName}}</div>
  <div>{{client.address}}</div>
  <div>{{client.cityStateZip}}</div>
  <div>DOB: {{client.dob}}</div>
  <div>SSN: XXX-XX-{{client.ssnLast4}}</div>
</div>

<div class="date">{{date}}</div>

<div class="to">
  <div>{{bureau.displayName}}</div>
  <div>{{bureau.addressLine1}}</div>
  <div>{{bureau.addressLine2}}</div>
</div>

<div class="titles">
  <div>AFFIDAVIT OF TRUTH:</div>
  <div>AFFIDAVIT OF DEMAND FOR DEBT VALIDATION</div>
  <div>AFFIDAVIT OF NOTICE OF WRONG PERSON</div>
  <div>AFFIDAVIT OF NOTICE OF RIGHT TO PUBLIC LAW: 48, 48 112</div>
  <div>AFFIDAVIT OF NOTICE OF IDENTITY THEFT VICTIM</div>
  <div>AFFIDAVIT OF NOTICE OF FRAUDULENT ACCOUNTS, LOANS, CREDIT CARDS, AND OTHER FINANCIAL INFORMATION</div>
</div>

<div class="opening">
  I, {{client.fullName}}, make oath and depose the following facts. I am an identity theft victim and I have absolutely no knowledge of the alleged debts listed on your website.
</div>

{{#if items.length}}
<div><strong>The following items appearing on my file with {{bureau.displayName}} are disputed:</strong></div>
<ul class="items">
{{#each items}}
  <li class="item">
    <div class="item-creditor">{{this.creditor}}</div>
    <div class="item-detail">{{this.detail}}</div>
  </li>
{{/each}}
</ul>
<div class="shared-reason">{{sharedReason}}</div>
{{/if}}

{{#if personalInfoItems.length}}
<div class="pi-section">
  <div><strong>Personal information disputes:</strong></div>
  <ul class="pi-list">
  {{#each personalInfoItems}}
    <li><strong>{{this.fieldLabel}}:</strong> "{{this.value}}" — {{this.reasonText}}</li>
  {{/each}}
  </ul>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div class="demand">
  Please block this information from my credit report, pursuant to section 605B of the Fair Credit Reporting Act, and send the required notifications to all furnishers of this information.
</div>

<div class="enclosed">
  <div>Enclosed are the following:</div>
  <ul>
    <li>A copy of my credit report I received from your company. The fraudulent items are circled.</li>
    <li>A copy of my Identity Theft Report and proof of my identity.</li>
    <li>A copy of section 605B of the Fair Credit Reporting Act, which requires you to block the fraudulent information on my credit report resulting from identity theft within <strong>four business days</strong> and to promptly notify the furnisher(s) of that information.</li>
    <li>Evidence of the data breach that exposed my personal information.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="closing">
  I appreciate your prompt attention to this matter, and await your reply.
</div>

<div class="longform">
  I am the eyewitness the information is incorrect and I demand the validation of all debts alleged to be mine listed on your website. I have attached a copy of an identity theft report filed with the Federal Trade Center and demand you cease and desist from the presentment of all information alleged to be mine in order to avoid any possible liable for the identity theft or data breach of personal information. I require a fraud alert on my account and all visible information completely blocked and deleted upon forwarding of the identity theft report. All creditors must be aware that if they were eyewitnesses to their allegations, then they must know who stole my identity and possibly conspired with the individual to steal my identity and attempt to hold me to fraudulent/unenforceable contracts which an entity cannot be an eyewitness to unless using deceptive practices in and affecting commerce in violation of the Fair Debt Collection Practices Act. I do not know any of the alleged creditors and debt collectors.
</div>

<div class="sign-off">Sincerely,</div>
<div class="signature-line"></div>
<div class="signature-name">{{client.fullName}}</div>

</body>
</html>
